@NewsRoom.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5005

### Health check
GET {{NewsRoom.Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Get available news categories
GET {{NewsRoom.Api_HostAddress}}/api/news/categories
Accept: application/json

### Get news articles (all categories, last 24h)
GET {{NewsRoom.Api_HostAddress}}/api/news?timePeriodHours=24&maxArticles=7
Accept: application/json

### Get news articles (filtered by categories)
GET {{NewsRoom.Api_HostAddress}}/api/news?timePeriodHours=12&categories=Inrikes,Utrikes,Sport&maxArticles=5
Accept: application/json

### Start a new broadcast generation
POST {{NewsRoom.Api_HostAddress}}/api/broadcast
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "timePeriodHours": 24,
  "categories": ["Inrikes", "Utrikes", "Sport", "Politik", "Ekonomi"],
  "maxArticles": 7
}

### Get broadcast job status (replace {jobId} with actual ID)
GET {{NewsRoom.Api_HostAddress}}/api/broadcast/{jobId}
Accept: application/json

### Get recent broadcast jobs
GET {{NewsRoom.Api_HostAddress}}/api/broadcast/recent
Accept: application/json
